Commentary: overpitched on middle, and that's been swept away! Starting on a very positive note as deep midwicket fails to cut it off
Commentary_short: Badree to Liton Das, FOUR runs

Commentary: good length on middle, and Liton comes down the wicket. Checks his shot eventually
Commentary_short: Badree to Liton Das, no run

Commentary: good length on middle, and he backs away before pulling to long on for just a single
Commentary_short: Badree to Liton Das, 1 run

Commentary: full on leg stump, and Tamim shuffles across to the off side, before clipping this away to square leg

Commentary: back of a length on leg stump, and fended back to Badree off the back foot
Commentary_short: Badree to Liton Das, no run

Commentary: length ball on middle, and he makes room before pulling to the cow-corner region. Two fielders converge in that region to intercept the ball from going for a boundary

Commentary: length ball outside off, but angling into Tamim's pads. Defended to the off side

Commentary: full just outside off, and Tamim comes forward rather tentatively to defend
Commentary_short: Nurse to Tamim Iqbal, no run

Commentary: tossed up outside off, and Tamim manages to open his arms for the drive. Struck well, but only till the fielder at cover

Commentary: movement of the feet! Good length outside off, but Liton shuffles across, then swivels to open his stance, and finally pulls behind square for six more runs

Commentary: tossed up outside off, and Liton goes down on one knee to slog-sweep over midwicket. Just over the fingertips of the fielder as the ball races away to the boundary. Seventeen runs off that one!

Commentary: full outside off, and Tamim smothers a straight drive past Liton to long off
Commentary_short: Badree to Tamim Iqbal, 1 run

Commentary: full on leg stump, and he taps it away to midwicket for a comfortable single
Commentary_short: Badree to Liton Das, 1 run

Commentary: full outside off, but Tamim backs away to make some extra room, and then crunches a drive through the covers! Oh, glorious
Commentary_short: Badree to Tamim Iqbal, FOUR runs

Commentary: full outside off, and Tamim shuffles in his crease before eventually leaning into the front-foot drive to cover
Commentary_short: Badree to Tamim Iqbal, no run

Commentary: back of a length on middle, and Tamim opens his stance to pull. But it comes off the bat's toe end and dribbles back to Badree
Commentary_short: Badree to Tamim Iqbal, no run

Commentary: slog swept over cow corner! Hello there. Tossed up on middle, and down Tamim goes on one knee to send this over the boundary for half-a-dozen more

Commentary: good length on middle, and flicked off his hips over square leg for four more! Ball coming onto the bat real smooth tonight. Easy come easy go...

Commentary: full on off, but Liton comes down the wicket, effectively yorking himself. Mistimes a shot to the leg side for a jogging single

Commentary: back of a length on off, and Tamim's flat-batted pull comes off the bat's toe end. Intercepted at mid off

Commentary: short on off, and this pull is much more convincing! Settles onto the back foot, and simply chips this shot over the mid-wicket fielder for four more to their total

Commentary: full outside off,and angling into Liton. He swings through the ball's line and mistimes the on-drive to mid on
Commentary_short: Brathwaite to Liton Das, no run

Commentary: back of a length on middle, and he rides the bounce to defend off the back foot

Commentary: full outside off, and driven square to the sweeper fielder in the deep. Walton doing the heavy lifting there

Commentary: short on middle, but Liton manages to swivel and guide a check-pull down to fine leg for one. Moves to 48

Commentary: short! But Mushfiqur can't ramp it over the keeper's head. Misses out on the shot as the ball goes through to the keeper. Five singles in the over

Commentary: full on leg, and nudged to the vacant square-leg region off the back foot

Commentary: tossed up on off, and flicked to square leg once again as the two batsmen comfortably rotate the strike
Commentary_short: Badree to Mushfiqur Rahim, 1 run

Commentary: full on off, and he attempts the sweep over square leg. But he gloves the shot to short fine leg instead

Commentary: flat on off, and he punches this straight back to Badree! Could've been out, but Badree misses and that's Liton's first fifty in white-ball cricket!

Commentary: back of a length on middle, and worked back to Badree off the back foot
Commentary_short: Badree to Mushfiqur Rahim, no run

Commentary: length ball outside off, and he plays the late cut to third man
Commentary_short: Williams to Liton Das, 1 run
